lph is Dean of Washington National Cathedral — two Hollerith brothers at once in the church’s senior ranks."},{"number":2,"category":"religion","header":"Two brothers, two great pulpits","body":"While Holly led the Diocese of Southern Virginia, his younger brother Randolph became Dean of Washington National Cathedral — Hollerith brothers holding two of the Episcopal Church’s most visible posts at once."}],"cross_connections":[{"type":"family_connection","related_id":"I00272","display_label":"Great-grandson of Herman Hollerith, IBM founder and punch-card inventor","link_text":"Herman Hollerith Sr.","description":"Bishop Hollerith's great-grandfather was Herman Hollerith Sr., inventor of the electromechanical punched-card tabulating machine and founder of the Tabulating Machine Company that became IBM. The bishop's first name 'Herman' continues the four-generation family naming pattern (Herman Sr → Herman Jr → Herman III → Herman IV)."}],"bio":{"title":"Rt. Rev.","first_name":"Herman","last_name":"Hollerith","married_names":[],"suffix":"IV","nickname":"\"Holly\"","display_name":"Rt. Rev. Herman \"Holly\" Hollerith IV","photo_url":"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSXhg44fnRW57RcxE4Yl2CQbBYzRNtxmo44yyZ7SSYGRHuRNjT_H7YT_0fvF0Y2pvAYIPHzMlAeDHulL9KIRWw9aJlVFCG8TgMdwrImUQ&s=10"},"baptism":{},"research_tags":[],"research_sources":[],"documents":[],"naming_inspiration":[],"institutions":[{"institution_id":"INST121"}],"landmarks":[],"artworks":[],"quotes":[],"military_service":[],"slug":"herman-hollerith-iv-1955"}},"burialCemetery":null,"institutionsById":{},"crossConnections":[]}